<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title || 'Error del Servidor' %></title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .error-container {
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 90%;
        }
        
        .error-code {
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #f5576c;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .error-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .error-message {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .error-details {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-align: left;
            color: #888;
            max-height: 200px;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background: #f5576c;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background: #e74c3c;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #6c757d;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #5a6268;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding-top: 1rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        .debug-info {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-code">500</div>
        <h1 class="error-title">Error del Servidor</h1>
        
        <p class="error-message">
            Ha ocurrido un error interno en el servidor. Por favor, intenta nuevamente m치s tarde.
        </p>
        
        <% if (typeof stack !== 'undefined' && stack) { %>
            <div class="debug-info">
                <strong>Informaci칩n de desarrollo:</strong>
                <div class="error-details">
                    <%= stack %>
                </div>
            </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <div class="button-group">
            <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn btn-secondary">Volver Atr치s</a>
            <a href="/" class="btn">Recargar P치gina</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="contact-info">
            Si el problema persiste, por favor contacta al administrador del sitio.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>